org.apache.flink.contrib.streaming.state

类 RocksDBKeyedStateBackend.RocksDBMergeIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.contrib.streaming.state.RocksDBKeyedStateBackend.RocksDBMergeIterator
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable
    封闭类:
    RocksDBKeyedStateBackend<K>

    static final class RocksDBKeyedStateBackend.RocksDBMergeIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Iterator that merges multiple RocksDB iterators to partition all states into contiguous key-groups. The resulting iteration sequence is ordered by (key-group, kv-state).
